task.summary:
Fix logic on all gates and added tests
Changed all logic on gates to return the array outputs so they can be easily passed to other gates; this allows easier daisy-chaining. Had to change the interfaces for this to happen and added tests. The tests are simple junit tests.
Move Gate to class and fix up bit handling
Mux now returns data from selected line
Demux and demux test now working
Changed adder logic to perform bitwise operations to help with flags
Cleaned up adder logic, added test
Added OR gate functionality/testing and address label documentation
